rong><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Automated Notifications:</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"> Automatically trigger e-mails based on actions learners take (or don&rsquo;t take) in a course.</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:96px; text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Discussion Forums:</span></strong> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">Encourage conversation among learners by adding a course specific discussion forums.</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Leaderboards:</span></strong> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">Award and display the learners who obtain the best scores on quizzes in your courses.</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Badges &amp; Certificates:</span></strong> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">Award official certificates based on quiz performance, completing a course, or both!</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Course Points:</span></strong> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">Award points to learners as they complete lessons and allow learners to unlock new content.</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Assignments:</span></strong> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">Require assignment submissions before learners can continue to the next lessons.</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"3\" style=\"list-style-type:upper-alpha\">\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:22.0pt\">Marketing and Sales:&nbsp; </span></strong></span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">One-Time Purchases: </span></strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">Simply set a price and your course is ready to be purchased using PayPal, Stripe, or 2Checkout and others payment gateway.</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:72px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">Entice customers to purchase by offering free samples of your content. Your customers get accounts automatically right after purchase and they are enrolled into the course(s) they purchased.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:72px; text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Subscriptions:</span></strong><strong> </strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">Maximize your course revenue through recurring payments. You can set the payment schedule to anything you would like!</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:24px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">Choose to subscriptions for each course, or create a bundle of courses for a recurring price!</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:24px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">Built-in recurring payment functionality is available for PayPal, Stripe, and 2Checkout.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:24px; text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Shopping Cart:</span></strong><strong> </strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">Easily add a shopping cart experience for your courses by using one of our free WordPress shopping cart integrations (WooCommerce or Easy Digital Downloads).</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:24px; text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:72px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">Shopping carts allow you to use virtually any payment gateway, add coupons, discount codes, sales, course bundles, tax rules, custom receipts, sales funnels and more!</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:72px; text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Memberships:</span></strong><strong> </strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">Instead of selling access to individual courses, our membership capability let&rsquo;s you create various memberships that contain access to multiple courses. When someone purchases access to the membership then they get enrolled into all the courses associated with it.</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:72px; text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:72px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">You can choose to sell access for a one-time price, or on a recurring basis (i.e. $19 every month). You can even use a shopping cart (like WooCommerce) to sell membership access!</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:72px; text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:72px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Three type membership:</span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">Basic</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">Professional</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">Enterprise </span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Course Bundles: </span></strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">If you have multiple courses, you may want to sell bundles so that customers get access to more than one after purchase. This is easily accomplished in LearnDash!</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:72px; text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:72px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">Run flash sales that give customers access to more than one course, or give customers a discount if they purchase all the courses instead of one-by-one!</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:72px; text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Bulk Access: </span></strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">Allow customers to purchase licenses in bulk and then grant access to their staff. After purchase, the staff are all added to the same group where the Group Leader can track their progress and performance!</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"4\" style=\"list-style-type:upper-alpha\">\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:20.0pt\">Management:</span></strong></span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Group Management: </span></strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">Place users into groups and sub-groups, then allow others to manage.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\">Assig</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">nment Management: </span></strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">Approve, comment, and award points on submitted assignments.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Detailed Reporting: </span></strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">Quickly run reports on enrollment, progress, and performance.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Gradebook: </span></strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">Syncs with LearnDash quiz &amp; assignments, and manual grading.</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>', 'Order Now', 'active');
